IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. RATINGENGINE.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 L-BASE-PREMIUM    PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 1000.00.
       01 L-RIDER-PREMIUM   PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 200.00.
       01 L-TOTAL-PREMIUM   PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "RATING ENGINE START".

           COMPUTE L-TOTAL-PREMIUM = 
                L-BASE-PREMIUM + L-RIDER-PREMIUM.

           DISPLAY "BASE PREMIUM : " L-BASE-PREMIUM.
           DISPLAY "RIDER PREMIUM: " L-RIDER-PREMIUM.
           DISPLAY "TOTAL PREMIUM: " L-TOTAL-PREMIUM.

           DISPLAY "RATING ENGINE FINISHED".

           STOP RUN.